"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-07-olympic-athlete-making-onlyfans-rowing-thanks-artistic-nudes-21377926\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"New Zealand's Robbie Manson may have finished sixth at the Olympic Games in the men's double skulls, but he has been making more money out of OnlyFans than rowing.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 163, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 11, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.8991600686927564, \"rank\": 0.09201601951659134, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 14, \"end\": 27, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Manson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Robbie Manson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Manson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Manson\"}, {\"begin\": 142, \"end\": 150, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OnlyFans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"OnlyFans\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OnlyFans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OnlyFans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 55, \"to\": 72}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's double skulls\", \"from\": 76, \"to\": 99}, {\"ngram\": \"more money\", \"from\": 124, \"to\": 134}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Manson, along with teammateJordanParry, reached the final inParisand managed sixth place, which is especially remarkable as Manson retired from rowing in 2020, returning in 2022.\", \"from\": 165, \"to\": 343, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 165, \"end\": 171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marilyn_Manson\", \"score\": 0.9975648196587676, \"rank\": 0.0024411249205904596, \"text\": \"Manson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marilyn_Manson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marilyn_Manson\"}, {\"begin\": 289, \"end\": 295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marilyn_Manson\", \"score\": 0.9975648196587676, \"rank\": 0.0024411249205904596, \"text\": \"Manson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marilyn_Manson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marilyn_Manson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"teammateJordanParry\", \"from\": 184, \"to\": 203}, {\"ngram\": \"the final inParisand\", \"from\": 213, \"to\": 233}, {\"ngram\": \"sixth place\", \"from\": 242, \"to\": 253}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Away from the boat, the 34-year-old has been posing for OnlyFans content and he says he has been earning more through his racy photos than his races on water.\", \"from\": 345, \"to\": 503, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 401, \"end\": 409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OnlyFans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"OnlyFans\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OnlyFans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OnlyFans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the boat\", \"from\": 355, \"to\": 363}, {\"ngram\": \"his racy photos\", \"from\": 463, \"to\": 478}, {\"ngram\": \"his races\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 493}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 502}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I get more than double what I would be on otherwise as an athlete - read into that what you will, but I am making more from OnlyFans than I am from rowing at this stage,' Manson toldReuters.\", \"from\": 505, \"to\": 696, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 630, \"end\": 638, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OnlyFans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"OnlyFans\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OnlyFans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/OnlyFans\"}, {\"begin\": 677, \"end\": 683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marilyn_Manson\", \"score\": 0.9975648196587676, \"rank\": 0.0024411249205904596, \"text\": \"Manson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marilyn_Manson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marilyn_Manson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more than double what\", \"from\": 512, \"to\": 533}, {\"ngram\": \"this stage\", \"from\": 664, \"to\": 674}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I thought, if I am going to do it, you have to tell everyone, be really open and I think you need to feel that any publicity is good publicity.\", \"from\": 698, \"to\": 842, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 759}, {\"ngram\": \"any publicity\", \"from\": 810, \"to\": 823}, {\"ngram\": \"good publicity\", \"from\": 827, \"to\": 841}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The fact that I amgay, I have the gay following and the audience already, and I am slightly leaning into that.\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 955, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gay following\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 892}, {\"ngram\": \"the audience\", \"from\": 897, \"to\": 909}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I would not say it's for everyone, (but) for other athletes, there is definitely an opportunity there.'\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 1059, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 989}, {\"ngram\": \"other athletes\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1015}, {\"ngram\": \"an opportunity\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked what he generally posts on Only Fans, he said: 'Artistic nudes - I do not want to say too much more than that, I think people need to subscribe if they want to know what's exactly on there.\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1256, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Only Fans\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1103}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1192}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'But in the captions, I just try to give people a little bit of an update from time to time, like what's going on in my life or training or journey to this point, towards theOlympics.'\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1442, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the captions\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1278}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1305}, {\"ngram\": \"a little bit\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1318}, {\"ngram\": \"an update\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1331}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1341}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1349}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1382}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 1386, \"to\": 1394}, {\"ngram\": \"journey\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1405}, {\"ngram\": \"this point\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1419}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympics\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1440}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Manson posted an emotional message on social media after his Olympic exploits, thrilled with his return to elite rowing.\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1564, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1444, \"end\": 1450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marilyn_Manson\", \"score\": 0.9975648196587676, \"rank\": 0.0024411249205904596, \"text\": \"Manson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marilyn_Manson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marilyn_Manson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an emotional message\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1478}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1494}, {\"ngram\": \"his Olympic exploits\", \"from\": 1501, \"to\": 1521}, {\"ngram\": \"his return\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1547}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's hard to put into words what a journey this has been, but here goes,' he wrote onInstagram.\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1662, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"words\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1594}, {\"ngram\": \"what a journey\", \"from\": 1595, \"to\": 1609}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Four years ago, I retired, never imagining I'd get back in a rowing boat.\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1737, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a rowing boat\", \"from\": 1723, \"to\": 1736}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet here I am, not only back at the Olympics but in the A final!\", \"from\": 1738, \"to\": 1802, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1782}, {\"ngram\": \"the A final\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1801}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'While we are gutted that we could not clinch it today, I am incredibly proud that we made it to the top 6 at the Olympics-a first for both of us.\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1950, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 1926}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1947, \"to\": 1949}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The competition in the men's double field was tough, and I have huge respect and congratulations for our competitors.\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 2070, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The competition\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 1968}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's double field\", \"from\": 1972, \"to\": 1994}, {\"ngram\": \"huge respect\", \"from\": 2017, \"to\": 2029}, {\"ngram\": \"congratulations\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2049}, {\"ngram\": \"our competitors\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2069}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It was a great day for the team overall, with gold, silver, and bronze medals-so proud of our teammates.\", \"from\": 2072, \"to\": 2177, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a great day\", \"from\": 2080, \"to\": 2091}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 2096, \"to\": 2104}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 2119, \"to\": 2123}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2131}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze medals\", \"from\": 2137, \"to\": 2150}, {\"ngram\": \"our teammates\", \"from\": 2163, \"to\": 2176}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Jordan, you have been an incredible teammate!\", \"from\": 2179, \"to\": 2225, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an incredible teammate\", \"from\": 2202, \"to\": 2224}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You have kept me calm and reminded me not to take ourselves too seriously.\", \"from\": 2226, \"to\": 2300, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's been so much fun, and I am so proud of what we have accomplished together.\", \"from\": 2301, \"to\": 2380, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so much fun\", \"from\": 2311, \"to\": 2322}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We have had a very special M2x group with Jordan, Ben, Flynn, Jack, and myself over the past two years.\", \"from\": 2382, \"to\": 2486, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2425, \"end\": 2431, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"score\": 0.9833724236116459, \"rank\": 0.011386886085518117, \"text\": \"Jordan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\"}, {\"begin\": 2438, \"end\": 2443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Errol_Flynn\", \"score\": 0.999999408649903, \"rank\": 5.913337678436641e-07, \"text\": \"Flynn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Errol_Flynn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Errol_Flynn\"}, {\"begin\": 2445, \"end\": 2449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Shephard\", \"score\": 0.9255856296711727, \"rank\": 0.07934302107524534, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Shephard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Shephard\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very special M2x group\", \"from\": 2395, \"to\": 2419}, {\"ngram\": \"Ben\", \"from\": 2433, \"to\": 2436}, {\"ngram\": \"the past two years\", \"from\": 2467, \"to\": 2485}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have trained incredibly hard yet still tried to enjoy it, building a tight team that pushes and supports each other.\", \"from\": 2487, \"to\": 2606, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a tight team\", \"from\": 2557, \"to\": 2569}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ben, you have been a huge part of this journey too-thank you.\", \"from\": 2607, \"to\": 2668, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a huge part\", \"from\": 2626, \"to\": 2637}, {\"ngram\": \"this journey\", \"from\": 2641, \"to\": 2653}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Thanks to our coach, Gary, and all of the RNZ support team for helping us get here.\", \"from\": 2670, \"to\": 2754, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2713, \"end\": 2716, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RNZ\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"'Thanks\", \"from\": 2670, \"to\": 2677}, {\"ngram\": \"our coach\", \"from\": 2681, \"to\": 2690}, {\"ngram\": \"Gary\", \"from\": 2692, \"to\": 2696}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2742, \"to\": 2744}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And a massive thank you for all the support from back home and all over the world.'\", \"from\": 2755, \"to\": 2838, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"And a massive thank\", \"from\": 2755, \"to\": 2774}, {\"ngram\": \"all the support\", \"from\": 2783, \"to\": 2798}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2827, \"to\": 2836}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 2840, \"to\": 2888, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more stories\", \"from\": 2844, \"to\": 2856}, {\"ngram\": \"our sport page\", \"from\": 2873, \"to\": 2887}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 2890, \"to\": 2960, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Metro Sport\", \"from\": 2897, \"to\": 2908}, {\"ngram\": \"the latest news onFacebook\", \"from\": 2913, \"to\": 2939}, {\"ngram\": \"TwitterandInstagram